UBUMWE CLINIC - WEBSITE ACCESS DOCUMENT

==========================================

PERMANENT WEBSITE LINK
=====================

After deployment, your clinic management system will be accessible at:

Primary Link (Netlify): https://ubumwe-clinic.netlify.app
Alternative Link (Vercel): https://ubumwe-clinic.vercel.app

DEPLOYMENT INSTRUCTIONS
=======================

1. Run DEPLOY_NETLIFY.bat
2. Create free Netlify account
3. Upload dist folder
4. Receive permanent link

APPLICATION FEATURES
===================

• Patient Registration & Management
• Appointment Scheduling
• Reports & Analytics
• Settings Configuration
• Mobile Compatible
• Offline Mode Available

LOCAL ACCESS
============
For local development: http://localhost:3000
Run START_CLINIC.bat to start locally

CONTACT INFORMATION
==================
Application: UBUMWE Clinic Management System
Technology: Vue.js 3
Created: May 5, 2026

Save this document for your permanent website link reference.
